  "detailed_description": "<strong>\"How many deaths to clear?\" is a time attack game where players compete to clear the game as fast as possible while keeping track of the number of times they die.</strong><br><br><strong>Instructions for Controls</strong><br><br>　・While holding down the left mouse button, pull the cursor in the opposite direction of where you want to jump to make a bigger jump.<br>　・A prediction line will appear showing the direction you will be launched in.<br>　・Time slows down while the mouse button is held down.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/861c0880d0fc8dfbc2bc734dc3d465bf.poster.avif?t=1702477106\" width=582 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/861c0880d0fc8dfbc2bc734dc3d465bf.webm?t=1702477106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/861c0880d0fc8dfbc2bc734dc3d465bf.mp4?t=1702477106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>　・There is a limit to the number of times you can jump before you hit the ground and recover, so be careful not to waste your jumps.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/734c92b9b0780fe10b1e0a1bc65c4649.poster.avif?t=1702477106\" width=582 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/734c92b9b0780fe10b1e0a1bc65c4649.webm?t=1702477106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/734c92b9b0780fe10b1e0a1bc65c4649.mp4?t=1702477106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>　・Hitting a Flick Token that's been placed in the game will recover one jump.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/28dedd1435e8145c7177f3e0fc9aa2ef.poster.avif?t=1702477106\" width=582 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/28dedd1435e8145c7177f3e0fc9aa2ef.webm?t=1702477106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/28dedd1435e8145c7177f3e0fc9aa2ef.mp4?t=1702477106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Game Description</strong><br><br>　・If you hit a spike or laser, you will be sent back to the save point.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/850f42e49ce1a0db531774138dc12a42.poster.avif?t=1702477106\" width=582 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/850f42e49ce1a0db531774138dc12a42.webm?t=1702477106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/850f42e49ce1a0db531774138dc12a42.mp4?t=1702477106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>・Also, by touching certain objects placed along the way, you can update the save point.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/f973b38cee9cc1d0f5732fcc25c1e1f9.poster.avif?t=1702477106\" width=582 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/f973b38cee9cc1d0f5732fcc25c1e1f9.webm?t=1702477106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/f973b38cee9cc1d0f5732fcc25c1e1f9.mp4?t=1702477106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>That's it for the instructions.<br> <strong>Try to clear the game as fast as possible without dying too much, and enjoy the thrilling sensation that comes with it.</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>\"How many deaths to clear?\" is a time attack game where players compete to clear the game as fast as possible while keeping track of the number of times they die.</strong><br><br><strong>Instructions for Controls</strong><br><br>　・While holding down the left mouse button, pull the cursor in the opposite direction of where you want to jump to make a bigger jump.<br>　・A prediction line will appear showing the direction you will be launched in.<br>　・Time slows down while the mouse button is held down.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/861c0880d0fc8dfbc2bc734dc3d465bf.poster.avif?t=1702477106\" width=582 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/861c0880d0fc8dfbc2bc734dc3d465bf.webm?t=1702477106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/861c0880d0fc8dfbc2bc734dc3d465bf.mp4?t=1702477106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>　・There is a limit to the number of times you can jump before you hit the ground and recover, so be careful not to waste your jumps.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/734c92b9b0780fe10b1e0a1bc65c4649.poster.avif?t=1702477106\" width=582 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/734c92b9b0780fe10b1e0a1bc65c4649.webm?t=1702477106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/734c92b9b0780fe10b1e0a1bc65c4649.mp4?t=1702477106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>　・Hitting a Flick Token that's been placed in the game will recover one jump.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/28dedd1435e8145c7177f3e0fc9aa2ef.poster.avif?t=1702477106\" width=582 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/28dedd1435e8145c7177f3e0fc9aa2ef.webm?t=1702477106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/28dedd1435e8145c7177f3e0fc9aa2ef.mp4?t=1702477106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Game Description</strong><br><br>　・If you hit a spike or laser, you will be sent back to the save point.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/850f42e49ce1a0db531774138dc12a42.poster.avif?t=1702477106\" width=582 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/850f42e49ce1a0db531774138dc12a42.webm?t=1702477106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/850f42e49ce1a0db531774138dc12a42.mp4?t=1702477106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>・Also, by touching certain objects placed along the way, you can update the save point.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/f973b38cee9cc1d0f5732fcc25c1e1f9.poster.avif?t=1702477106\" width=582 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/f973b38cee9cc1d0f5732fcc25c1e1f9.webm?t=1702477106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406560/extras/f973b38cee9cc1d0f5732fcc25c1e1f9.mp4?t=1702477106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>That's it for the instructions.<br> <strong>Try to clear the game as fast as possible without dying too much, and enjoy the thrilling sensation that comes with it.</strong>",
